through the rain.

00:00:41.360 --> 00:00:47.860
And I marched through some sickness and some
heartache and pain.

00:00:47.880 --> 00:00:53.680
And I laid on the ground, and I looked up
at the sky,

00:00:53.680 --> 00:00:58.859
and I prayed to Lord up above and asked why.

00:00:58.859 --> 00:01:05.100
But oh no, I'm not tired, I'm not through
marching yet,

