my granddaddy too.

00:02:04.320 --> 00:02:09.740
And I never thought it'd be something that
I'd have to do.

00:02:09.740 --> 00:02:12.520
But I'll march if I must.

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:16.019
I got a mission, you see.

00:02:16.019 --> 00:02:21.510
And I'll be damned if my children have to
march for me.

